channel.title: Could someone help me...willing to pay
channel.description: Ok so i have been downloading client sources and trying to get them to work...but i just cant...this is my first ever time trying to make my own rsc server...so my request is for someone to please help me set up a client source...im not asking for someone to help me code it because im a good coder...altho i have never coded in java before i am a quick learner...pretty much i am asking someone to help me find a source that works...and set it up to run off my computer untill i finish coding it when i can add it to my server...also i will need help with downloading and installing jdk because i have installed a bunch of the jdk versions but couldnt get them to work right...also finding the right apache ant and wampserver...i always got javac and ant errors...im willing to pay someone to help me out...willing to discuse amount to be paid...if interested message me on aim at shadowz0flife or msn at rich4lyfe@msn.com...please no spamming because i honostly have been trying to figure this out on my own but since i have never made a rsc server before and never set one up i dont know what im doing...but as i said im a quick learner...soon as i am shown how to do it i will understand and know how to do it for the future
